# Auto-generated YouTube thumbnail caches.
# Both paths are regenerated by `npm run download-heroes` (prebuild hook,
# which mirrors a single download into both directories) and persisted
# across Netlify builds via netlify-plugin-cache. Don't commit these.
src/assets/hero-cache/*.jpg
src/assets/images/hero-cache/*.jpg

